727459f-b.text:
National Street, at the N.W. corner of 42nd Street, showing the Union Evangelical Church. It was built in 1871. Charles P. Leverich donated the site and edifice providing that it remain forever undenominational and free. View 1: Eugene L. Armbruster Collection April,1925
Views 2,3: P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS  October 2, 1935
